https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/36DgXVxjyPigRdgKyElhhHv06Zt.jpg A documentary about the 1973-74 Miami Dolphins and their return to the Super Bowl. The previous year they had completed a perfect undefeated season, but even so after this Super Bowl Coach Don Shula said “I think that we’re a better team than we were a year ago at this time.” They didn’t just defend their world title, they pummeled their opponents while doing so.
